{"tid":1322064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新城市死口唔認好戇鳩","createTime":"2019-07-16T00:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T01:39:20.000Z","uid":52605,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0871e0f867cbfb103fa7f37665b49f680f556b28","tid":1322064,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBkdxyj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBkdxyj.png&h=8fad4679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死撐有乜用<br />\n黑警另一面就同傳媒講話一早聯絡咗商場<br />\n你哋想食兩家茶禮個算盤打唔響"},{"pid":"85ce34350336ab710315d25dc803037d1ee2cf6b","tid":1322064,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:36:18.000Z","msg":"想睇埋篇新聞落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最終點"},{"pid":"843c0e8cdcf59bf1bb350ce1281a69fc8447ac8e","tid":1322064,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"認真 唔好比警犬帶風向 分化到<br />\n商場事前同警犬開過會係事實，但亦都係有大型公眾event時既慣常做法，因為要同遊行牽涉地方既負責人商討、協調<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但咁樣唔代表新地知晒成個警犬部署同行動<br />\n事實就係果一刻警犬係突擊，商場毫不知情<br />\n<br />\n警犬話事前同新地商討過 完全係混淆視聽 將個波推返落新地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n新地仆街固然係事實<br />\n但矛頭係警犬，唔好比人帶到風向"}]}